<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>{% include "court_base.css" %}</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-block">
        <strong>Date:</strong> {{ date_of_draft }}<br><br>
        <strong>To,</strong><br>
        The Director / Coordinator,<br>
        {{ ngo_name | default("Concerned NGO") }}<br>
        {{ ngo_address | default("Bengaluru, Karnataka") }}
    </div>

    <div class="subject-line">
        SUBJECT: Referral for Emergency Assistance and Support Services
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        Dear Sir/Madam,
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        This letter is to formally refer <strong>{{ applicant_name }}</strong> to your organization for emergency assistance. The individual is currently experiencing a crisis and requires immediate support services.
    </div>

    <h2>Referred Person Details</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Name</th><td>{{ applicant_name }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Age</th><td>{{ applicant_age | default("") }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Contact</th><td>{{ applicant_phone | default("") }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Crisis Category</th><td>{{ crisis_category | default("") }}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Situation Summary</h2>
    <div class="body-text">
        {{ draft_body_summary }}
    </div>

    <h2>Services Requested</h2>
    <div class="body-text">
        <ul>
            <li>Emergency shelter / safe accommodation</li>
            <li>Counselling and emotional support</li>
            <li>Legal assistance coordination</li>
            <li>Livelihood support and rehabilitation</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
        We request your organization to extend all necessary support and assistance to the referred individual at the earliest.
    </div>

    <div class="signature-block">
        <div class="line"></div>
        <strong>Sahayak — Last Mile Justice Navigator</strong><br>
        Automated Referral System<br>
        Date: {{ date_of_draft }}
    </div>
</body>
</html>
